			<li>Plaxo should now display a message that says "Your contacts have been added".  Click the "Done" button.  You can now use these contacts to easily send emails to your friends.  See instructions below for managing your contacts list and creating email groups.</li><br>
			 		
		</ol>	
	</ol>			

<strong><li class="about">Managing Your Email Contacts</li></strong>

<ol start="A" type="A">
	<strong><li>Creating an Email Group</li></strong>

	<ol start="1" type="1">
		<li>Once signed in to your account, click on the “Profile” link in the upper right hand corner of the website.</li><br>
	
		<li>If you haven't already, Import your contacts using the steps outlined in the section above.</li><br>
	
		<li>Click on the <img src="<%= root_url %>images/About/Manage Contacts.jpg"> button in the “EMAIL SETTINGS” section in the lower right hand corner of the page.</li><br>
	
		<li>Check the boxes of the contacts you'd like to add to a group and then click the <img src="<%= root_url %>images/About/Add to Group.jpg"> button at the top of the list of contacts</li><br>
	
		<li>Click the radio button next to "New Group" and then type the name of the group in the box to the right and click the "Add Contacts" button.</li><br>
	</ol>
	
	<strong><li>Removing a Contact From a Group</li></strong>
	<ol start="1" type="1">
		<li>Once you've added an email group, it will show up in a menu to the left of your list of contacts.  To remove a contact from a group, click on the group you wish to remove that contact from.  The site will display a full list of contacts included in that group.</li><br>
		<li>Click on the check box next to the contact you wish to remove from the group and then click the <img src="<%= root_url %>images/About/Remove From Group.jpg"> button above the list of contacts.  This will remove the contact from the group but will not delete the contact from your Contacts list.</li><br>
	</ol>
	
	<strong><li>Adding a New Contact</li></strong>
	<ol start="1" type="1">
		<li>Click on the <img src="<%= root_url %>images/About/New Contact.jpg"> button in the top right hand side of the "Contacts" page.</li><br>
		<li>Enter the Contact's Name and Email into the pop up and click "Submit".</li><br>
	</ol>
	
	<strong><li>Deleting a Contact</li></strong>
	<ol start="1" type="1">
		<li>Click on the check box next to the contact you wish to delete (you can select multiple contacts to delete) and then click the <img src="<%= root_url %>images/About/Delete Selected.jpg"> button above the list of contacts.  This will permanently remove the contact(s) from your Contacts list.</li><br>
		<li>If you want to add this contact back in the future, you can either add it through the "New Contact" or "Import Contacts" feature.</li><br>
	</ol>
	
	<strong><li>Editing a Contact</li></strong>
	<ol start="1" type="1">
		<li>Click on the <img src="<%= root_url %>images/About/Edit.jpg"> button to the right of the contact that you want to change.  This will bring up a pop up box with that contact's name and email address.</li><br>
		<li>Make your changes and then click the "Submit" button.</li>
	</ol>
	

